event.title: Empowering Open Source Contributors and Building Future Leaders
event.metaTitle: Empowering Open Source Contributors and Building Future Leaders
event.metaDesc: In this Twitter Space with CHAOSS Project Africa, we will hear from some maintainers who actively contribute and maintain the CHAOSS Project talk about their journey, and how they navigate their daily lives as a maintainer.
event.content: In this Twitter Space with CHAOSS Project Africa, we will hear from some maintainers who actively contribute and maintain the CHAOSS Project talk about their journey, and how they navigate their daily lives as a maintainer.
